di bawah mentari ♪

323
00:31:22,540 --> 00:31:26,141
Makan.

324
00:31:31,148 --> 00:31:33,782
Kau membuat temanmu tewas.

325
00:31:33,784 --> 00:31:35,450
Aku membuat Tina tewas.

326
00:31:35,452 --> 00:31:39,588
Dan jangan berpura-pura
seolah kau tak tahu nilainya.

327
00:31:48,766 --> 00:31:51,166
Kau seharusnya mati.

328
00:31:51,168 --> 00:31:55,003
Tapi Negan memperhatikanmu.

329
00:31:55,005 --> 00:31:57,439
Kau beruntung.

330
00:31:57,441 --> 00:31:59,808
Jangan lupa.

331
00:32:04,515 --> 00:32:06,949
Selamat makan.

