00:33:30,501 --> 00:33:33,869
♪ Kau tak bisa tahu ♪

340
00:33:33,871 --> 00:33:40,509
♪ Bahwa aku telah menangisimu ♪

341
00:33:40,511 --> 00:33:45,280
♪ Menangisimu ♪

342
00:33:45,282 --> 00:33:49,918
♪ Ketika kau mengatakan,
